Louise Germaine https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Louise_Germaine 0 Tina Louise Germaine (born 1971, in Margate, Kent) is an English actress and model best known for her appearance as usherette Sylvia Berry in the 1993 Dennis Potter serial Lipstick on Your Collar. She played chambermaid Kate Hargreaves in the six-part 1994 comedy House Of Windsor.
